{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"db9f16e3-c995-4644-8de2-67f545fd5078","content":"Your `.testsettings` file is a **legacy format** that modern MSTest (v3+) no longer processes. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your settings map to:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30s) | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / deployment | Not needed (modern MSTest handles this) |\n| Code Coverage `DataCollector` | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n\nLet me create the replacement files:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01HLHQL1EmDGHHPTa6N7Xtxx","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating .runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01BjyGF3U4uSU5C2rhyT9fv1","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-cd344b23644e43aea81aa2c7f995460a/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n  <RunConfiguration>\n    <TestSessionTimeout>30000</TestSessionTimeout>\n  </RunConfiguration>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-cd344b23644e43aea81aa2c7f995460a/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01NdnTMt7tujnVaQGjKjDBhV","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-cd344b23644e43aea81aa2c7f995460a/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>","new_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\local.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n  </PropertyGroup>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-cd344b23644e43aea81aa2c7f995460a/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"9d0afbf3-19c9-41bb-8ca3-26946580c360","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file which is a legacy format. With MSTest v3+, the recommended approach is to use a `.runsettings` file instead. Let me explain the migration.\n\nThe `.testsettings` file contains:\n1. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext=\"true\"` — deployment-related, not needed in modern MSTest\n2. `TestTimeout` of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. Code Coverage data collector\n\nI need to create a `.runsettings` file that replaces this configuration.","outputTokens":844,"requestId":"083B:1FFE72:56BBD2:659D6A:69EAD3CA"},"id":"52b85456-6335-46c9-a3c9-ff091d4c69d6","timestamp":"2026-04-24T02:22:15.635Z","parentId":"9065381d-6112-4ab8-abc9-33708b4a31a8"}
